Anthony Raborn was born in 1990 in Lake Wales, Florida. He graduated from the University of Florida with the Bachelor of Science in psychology and the Bachelor of Arts in political science in 2012 and the Master of Arts in Education in Research and Evaluation Methodology in 2016. His major non-academic interests include reading science fiction and fantasy novels and playing video games. He will be continuing his education, working towards a doctoral degree in the same field.
